<?php
$t = array();
$t[1] = 'Y&atilde; ku mut&atilde;ne! Ku bi Ubangijinku da taƙawa. Lalle ne girgizar ƙasa ta tsayuwar Sa\'a wata aba ce mai girma.';
$t[2] = 'A r&atilde;nar da kuke ganin ta dukan mai sh&atilde;yar da m&atilde;ma tan&atilde; shagala daga abin da ta sh&atilde;yar, kuma dukan mai ciki tan&atilde; haihuwar cikinta, kuma kan&atilde; ganin mut&atilde;ne sun&atilde; m&atilde;su m&atilde;yẽ alh&atilde;li kuwa su b&atilde; m&atilde;su m&atilde;ye ba, amma az&atilde;bar Allah ce mai tsanani.';
$t[3] = 'Akwai daga mut&atilde;ne wanda yake yin musũ ga sha\'anin Allah b&atilde; da wani ilmi ba, kuma yan&atilde; biyar k&otilde;wane Shaiɗan mai taurin kai.';
$t[4] = 'An wajabta masa cẽwa wanda ya jiɓince shi, to, lalle ne sai ya ɓatar da shi, kuma ya shiryar da shi zuwa ga az&atilde;bar sa\'ĩr.';
$t[5] = 'Ya ku mut&atilde;ne! Idan kun kasance a cikin shakka a T&atilde;shin &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma, to, lalle ne Mũ, Man halittaku daga turɓaya, sa\'an nan kuma daga gud&atilde;jin jini, sa\'an nan kuma daga ta&otilde;ka wadda ake halitt&atilde;wa da wadda ba a halittawa d&otilde;min, Mu bayyana muku. Kuma Mun&atilde; tab batar da abin da Muke so a cikin mahaifa zuwa ga wani ajali ambatacce, sa\'an nan kuma Mun&atilde; fitar da ku kun&atilde; j&atilde;rĩri, sa\'an nan kuma d&otilde;min ku kai ga cikar ƙarfinku. Kuma daga cikin ku akwai wanda ke mutuwa, kuma daga gare ku akwai wanda ake mayarwa zuwa ga mafi ƙasƙancin r&atilde;yuwa d&otilde;min kada ya san k&otilde;me a b&atilde;yan ya sani. Kuma kan&atilde; ganin ƙasa shiru, sa\'an nan idan Muka saukar da ruwa a kanta, sai ta girgiza kuma ta kumbura, kuma ta tsirar da tsirrai daga k&otilde;wane nau\'i mai ban sha\'awa.';
$t[6] = 'Wancan ne d&otilde;min lalle Allah Shi ne Gaskiya, kuma lalle ne shi Yake r&atilde;yar da matattu, kuma lalle Shi Mai ikon yi ne a kan k&otilde;me.';
$t[7] = 'Kuma lalle ne Sa\'ar T&atilde;shin &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma mai zuwa ce, b&atilde;bu shakka a cikinta kuma lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; t&atilde;yar da waɗanda suke a cikin ƙaburbura.';
$t[8] = 'Kuma daga mut&atilde;ne akwai mai yin musu ga Allah b&atilde; da wani ilmi ba kuma b&atilde; da wata shiriya ba, kuma b&atilde; da wani litt&atilde;fi mai haskak&atilde;wa ba.';
$t[9] = 'Yan&atilde; mai karkatar da s&atilde;shensa d&otilde;min ya ɓatar (da wasu) daga tafarkin Allah! Yan&atilde; da wani wul&atilde;kanci a dũniya, kuma Mun&atilde; ɗanɗana masa az&atilde;bar g&otilde;bara a R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma.';
$t[10] = '(A ce masa): &quot;Wancan azaba sab&otilde;da abin da hannayenka biyu suka gabatar ne, kuma lalle ne Allah bai zama Mai z&atilde;lunci ga b&atilde;yinSa ba.&quot;';
$t[11] = 'Kuma daga mut&atilde;ne akwai mai bauta wa Allah a kan wani gefe. Sa\'an nan idan wani alhẽri ya s&atilde;me shi, sai ya natsu da shi, kuma idan wata fitina ta s&atilde;me shi, sai ya jũya b&atilde;ya a kan fuskarsa. Y&atilde; yi has&atilde;rar dũniya da L&atilde;hira. Waccan ita ce has&atilde;ra bayyananna.';
$t[12] = 'Yan&atilde; kiran baicin Allah, abin da b&atilde; ya cũtarsa da abin da b&atilde; ya amf&atilde;ninsa! waccan ita ce ɓata mai nĩsa.';
$t[13] = 'Yan&atilde; kiran wanda yake lalle cũtarwarsa ce mafi kusa daga amf&atilde;ninsa! Lalle ne, tir da shi ya zama majiɓinci, kuma tir da ya zama ab&otilde;kin zama!';
$t[14] = 'Lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; shigar da waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai a cikin gid&atilde;jen Aljanna, ƙoramu na gud&atilde;na daga ƙarƙashinsu. Lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; aikata abin da Yake nufi.';
$t[15] = 'Wanda ya kasance yan&atilde; zaton cẽwa Allah b&atilde; zai taimake shi ba a cikin dũniya da L&atilde;hira to sai ya mĩƙa wata igiya zuwa sama, sa\'an nan kuma ya yanke ta, sa\'an nan ya dũba. Shin, ko lalle kaidinsa zai gusar da abin da yake ji na takaici?';
$t[16] = 'Kuma kamar haka Muka saukar da shi (Alƙur\'&atilde;ni) yan&atilde; &atilde;y&otilde;yi bayyanannu. Kuma lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; shiryar da wanda Yake nufi.';
$t[17] = 'Lalle ne waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni da waɗanda suka tũba (Yahũdu) da waɗanda suka karkace (Saba\'&atilde;wa) da Nas&atilde;ra da Majũs&atilde;wa da waɗanda suka yi shirka, lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; yin hukunci a tsak&atilde;ninsu a Ran&atilde;r &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma. Lalle ne Allah Mahalarci ne a kan dukkan k&otilde;me.';
$t[18] = 'Ashe, ba ka gani ba, lalle Allah, wanda yake a cikin sammai da wanda yake a cikin ƙasa yan&atilde; yin sujada a gare shi, da kuma r&atilde;na da wat&atilde; da taur&atilde;ri da duw&atilde;tsu da it&atilde;ce da dabb&otilde;bi, da kuma m&atilde;su yawa daga mut&atilde;ne? Kuma waɗansu m&atilde;su yawa az&atilde;ba t&atilde; tabbata a kansu. Kuma wanda Allah Ya wul&atilde;kantar, to, b&atilde; ya da wani mai girmam&atilde;wa. Kuma Lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; aikata abin da Yake so.';
$t[19] = 'waɗannan ƙungiy&otilde;yi biyu ne m&atilde;su husũma, sun yi husũma ga sha\'anin Ubangijinsu. To, waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta an yanka musu waɗansu tufafi daga wata irin wuta, an&atilde; zuba tafasasshen ruwa daga bisa k&atilde;wunansu.';
$t[20] = 'Da shĩ ake narkar da abin da yake a cikin cikunansu da f&atilde;tun jikinsu.';
$t[21] = 'Kuma sun&atilde; da waɗansu gwalm&otilde;min dũka na baƙin ƙarfe.';
$t[22] = 'A k&otilde;yaushe suka yi nufin fita daga gare ta, daga baƙin ciki, sai a mayar da su a cikinta, (a ce musu) &quot;Ku ɗanɗani az&atilde;bar g&otilde;bara.&quot;';
$t[23] = 'Lalle ne, Allah Yana shigar da waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai a cikin gid&atilde;jen Aljanna, ƙoramu sun&atilde; gud&atilde;na daga ƙarƙashinsu, an&atilde; ƙaw&atilde;ta su, a cikinsu, da waɗansu mund&atilde;ye na zĩn&atilde;ri da lu\'u-lu\'u. Kuma tuf&atilde;finsu a cikinsu alharĩni ne.';
$t[24] = 'Kuma an shiryar da su zuwa ga mai kyau na zance kuma an shiryar da su zuwa ga, hanyar wanda ake gode wa.';
$t[25] = 'Lalle ne waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta kuma suka taushe (mut&atilde;ne) daga hanyar Allah da masallaci mai alfarma wanda Muka sanya shi ga mut&atilde;ne alh&atilde;li kuwa mazauni a ciki da baƙauye daidai suke kuma wanda ya yi nufin karkatar da gaskiya a cikinsa da z&atilde;lunci z&atilde; Mu ɗanɗana masa daga wata az&atilde;ba mai raɗadi.';
$t[26] = 'Kuma a l&otilde;kacin da Muka iy&atilde;kance wa Ibr&atilde;him wurin &brvbar;akin (Muka ce masa), &quot;Kada ka haɗa k&otilde;me da Ni ga bauta, kuma ka tsarkake &brvbar;&atilde;kiNa d&otilde;min m&atilde;su ɗaw&atilde;fi da m&atilde;su tsayuwa da m&atilde;su ruku\'u da m&atilde;su sujada.';
$t[27] = '&quot;Kuma ka yi yẽkuwa ga mut&atilde;ne da wajabcin Hajji su je maka suna m&atilde;su tafiya da ƙaf&atilde;fu da kuma a kan k&otilde;wane maɗankwarin r&atilde;ƙumi m&atilde;su zuwa daga k&otilde;wane rango mai zurfi.&quot;';
$t[28] = '&quot;D&otilde;min su halarci abũbuwan amf&atilde;ni a gare su, kuma su amb&atilde;ci sunan Allah a cikin \'yan kw&atilde;nuka sanannu sab&otilde;da abin da Ya azurta su da shĩ daga dabb&otilde;bin jin d&atilde;ɗi. Sai ku ci daga gare su, kuma ku ciyar da matsattse matalauci.&quot;';
$t[29] = '&quot;Sa\'an nan kuma sai su ƙ&atilde;re ib&atilde;darsu da gusar da ƙazanta, knma sai su cika alkawuransu kuma sai su yi ɗaw&atilde;fi (sun&atilde; gẽwaya) ga &brvbar;&atilde;kin nin \'yantacce.&quot;';
$t[30] = 'Wancan ne. Kuma wanda ya girmama hukunce-hukuncen Allah to shĩ ne mafĩfĩci a gare shi, a wurin Ubangijinsa. Kuma an halatta muku dabb&otilde;bin ni\'ima f&atilde;ce abin da ake karant&atilde;wa a kanku. Sab&otilde;da haka ku nĩsanci ƙazanta daga gum&atilde;ka kuma ku nĩsanci ƙazanta daga shaidar zur.';
$t[31] = 'Kuna m&atilde;su tsayuwa ga gaskiya d&otilde;min Allah, ba masu yin shirka da Shi ba. Kuma wanda ya yi shirka da Allah, to, yan&atilde; kamar abin da ya f&atilde;ɗo daga sama, sa\'an nan tsunts&atilde;ye su cafe shi, ko iska ta f&atilde;ɗa da shi a cikin wani wuri mai nisa.';
$t[32] = 'Wancan ne. Kuma wanda ya girmama ib&atilde;d&otilde;din Allah, to, lalle ne ita (girmam&atilde;war) tan&atilde; daga ayyukan zuk&atilde;ta na ib&atilde;da.';
$t[33] = 'Kuna da waɗansu abũbuwan amf&atilde;ni a cikinta (dabbar hadaya) har ya zuwa ga wani ajali ambatacce, sa\'an nan kuma wurin halatt&atilde;ta zuwa ga &brvbar;&atilde;kin \'yantacce ne.';
$t[34] = 'Kuma ga k&otilde;wace al\'umma Mun sanya ib&atilde;dar yanka, d&otilde;min su ambaci sũnan Allah a kan abin da Ya azurta su da shi daga dabb&otilde;bin ni\'ima. Sa\'an nan kuma Abin bautawarku Abin bautawa ne Guda, sai ku sallama Masa. Kuma ka yi bush&atilde;ra ga m&atilde;su ƙanƙantar da kai.';
$t[35] = 'Waɗanda suke idan an ambaci Allah sai zuk&atilde;tansu su firgita, da m&atilde;su haƙuri a kan abin da ya s&atilde;me su, da m&atilde;su tsayar da salla, kuma sun&atilde; ciyarwa daga abin da Muka azurta su.';
$t[36] = 'Kuma r&atilde;ƙuman, Mun sanya su a gare ku, a ib&atilde;d&otilde;jin Allah. Kun&atilde; da wani alhẽri babba a cikinsu. Sai ku ambaci sũnan Allah a kansu sun&atilde; tsaye a kan ƙaf&atilde;fu uku. Sa\'an nan idan s&atilde;sanninsu suka f&atilde;ɗi, to, ku ci daga gare su, kuma ku ciyar da mai wadar zũci da mai bara. Kamar haka Muka h&otilde;re muku su, tsamm&atilde;ninku kun&atilde; g&otilde;dẽwa.';
$t[37] = 'N&atilde;m&otilde;minsu b&atilde; za su s&atilde;mi Allah ba haka jinainansu amma taƙawa daga gare ku tan&atilde;, s&atilde;mun Sa. Kamar haka Ya h&otilde;re su sab&otilde;da ku d&otilde;min ku girmama Allah sab&otilde;da shiriyar da Ya yi muku. Kuma ka yi bush&atilde;ra ga m&atilde;su kyautata yi.';
$t[38] = 'Lalle ne, Allah Yan&atilde; yin faɗa sab&otilde;da waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni. Lalle ne Allah b&atilde; Ya son dukkan mayaudari, mai yawan k&atilde;firci.';
$t[39] = 'An yi izni ga waɗanda ake y&atilde;ƙar su da cẽwa lalle an z&atilde;lunce su, kuma lalle ne Allah, haƙĩƙa, Mai ĩkon yi ne a kan taimakonsu.';
$t[40] = 'Waɗanda aka fitina daga gidajensu b&atilde; da wani hakki ba f&atilde;ce sun&atilde; cẽwa, Ubangijinmu Allah ne.&quot;Kuma ba d&otilde;min tunkuɗẽwar Allah ga mut&atilde;ne ba, s&atilde;shensu da s&atilde;she, haƙĩƙa, da an rũsa sauma\'&otilde;\'in (Ruhb&atilde;n&atilde;wa) d&atilde; maj&atilde;mi\'&otilde;\'in Nas&atilde;ra da gid&atilde;jen ib&atilde;dar Yahudu da masallatai waɗanda ake ambatar Allah a cikinsu da yawa. Kuma lalle, haƙĩƙa, Allah Yan&atilde; taimakon wanda yake taimakon Sa. Lalle Allah ne haƙĩƙa Mai ƙarfi Mabuw&atilde;yi.';
$t[41] = 'Waɗanda suke idan Muka b&atilde; su ĩko a cikin ƙasa sai su tsai da salla, kuma su baybr da zakka kuma su yi umurni da abin da aka sani, kuma su hana daga abin da ba a sani ba. Kuma &atilde;ƙibar al\'amura ga Allah take.';
$t[42] = 'Kuma idan sun ƙaryata ka, to lalle haƙĩƙa, mut&atilde;nen Nũhu da &Atilde;d&atilde;wa da Samũdawa, sun ƙaryata a gabaninsu.';
$t[43] = 'Da mut&atilde;nen Ibrahim da mut&atilde;nen Lũɗu.';
$t[44] = 'Da m&atilde;su Madyana, kuma an ƙaryata Mũs&atilde;. Sai Na jinkirtawa k&atilde;firan, sa\'an nan kuma Na k&atilde;ma su. To, y&atilde;ya musũNa (gare su) ya kasance?';
$t[45] = 'Sa\'an nan da yawa daga alƙarya, Muka halaka ta, alh&atilde;li kuwa tan&atilde; mai zalũnci sai ta zama f&atilde;ɗaɗɗa a kan rassanta, da yawa daga rĩjiya wadda aka w&otilde;fintar, da kuma gid&atilde;jen sarauta maɗaukaka.';
$t[46] = 'Shin, to, ba su yi tafiya ba a cikin ƙasa d&otilde;min zuk&atilde;ta waɗanda z&atilde; su yi hankali da su da kunnuwa da za su yi saur&atilde;re da su su kasance a gare su? D&otilde;min lalle ne id&atilde;nun ba su makanta, amma zuk&atilde;ta waɗanda ke a cikin ƙir&atilde;za sũ ke makanta.';
$t[47] = 'Kuma sun&atilde; nẽman ka yi gagg&atilde;wa da az&atilde;ba, alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah b&atilde; zai s&atilde;ɓa wa\'adinSa ba kuma lalle ne, yini ɗaya a wurin Ubangijinka kamar shẽkara dubu yake daga abin da kuke ƙid&atilde;y&atilde;wa.';
$t[48] = 'Kuma da yawa daga alƙarya, Na yi jinkirin az&atilde;ba gare ta (da laifinta) sa\'an nan Na k&atilde;ma ta, kuma zuwa gare Ni mak&otilde;ma take.';
$t[49] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Ya ku mut&atilde;ne! Nĩ wani mai gargaɗi ne kawai zuwa gare ku, mai bayyanawa.&quot;';
$t[50] = 'To, waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyuka na ƙwarai, sun&atilde; da g&atilde;fara da arziki na karimci.';
$t[51] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka yi aikin ɓ&atilde;t&atilde;wa a cikin ay&otilde;yinMu, sun&atilde; m&atilde;su gajiyarwa, waɗancan \'yan Jahĩm ne.';
$t[52] = 'Kuma ba Mu aika wani manzo ba a gab&atilde;ninka, kuma ba Mu umurci wani Annabi ba f&atilde;ce idan ya yi bũri, sai Shaiɗan ya jẽfa (wani abu) a cikin bũrinsa, sa\'an nan Allah Ya sh&atilde;fe abin da Shaiɗan ke jef&atilde;wa. Sa\'an nan kuma Allah Ya kyautata &atilde;y&otilde;yinSa. Kuma Allah Masani ne, Mai hikima.';
$t[53] = 'D&otilde;min Ya sanya abin da Shaiɗan ke jẽf&atilde;wa ya zama fitina ga waɗanda a cikin zuk&atilde;tansu akwai cũta, da m&atilde;su ƙẽƙasassun zuk&atilde;tansu. Kuma lalle ne azz&atilde;lumai haƙĩƙa, sun&atilde; a cikin s&atilde;ɓ&atilde;nimai nĩsa.';
$t[54] = 'Kuma d&otilde;min waɗanda aka bai wa ilmi su sani lalle shi ne gaskiya daga Ubangijinka d&otilde;min su yi ĩm&atilde;ni da shi sab&otilde;da zuk&atilde;tansu su natsu gare shi. Kuma lalle ne Allah, haƙĩƙa, Mai shiryar da waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni ne zuwa ga hanya madaidaiciya.';
$t[55] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta b&atilde; z&atilde; su gushe ba sun&atilde; a cikin shakka daga gare shi, har Sa\'a ta jẽ musu bisa ga abke, k&otilde; kuwa az&atilde;bar wani yini bakar&atilde;re ta jẽ musu.';
$t[56] = 'Mulki a r&atilde;nar nan ga Allah yake, Yan&atilde; hukunci a tsak&atilde;ninsu. To, waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai, sun&atilde; a cikin gid&atilde;jen Aljannar ni\'ima.';
$t[57] = 'Kuma waɗandra suka k&atilde;firta kuma suka ƙaryata, game da &atilde;y&otilde;yinMu, to, waɗannan sun&atilde; da az&atilde;ba mai wul&atilde;kantarwa.';
$t[58] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka yi hijira a cikin tafarkin Allah sa\'an nan kuma aka kashe su, k&otilde; suka mutu, lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; azurta su da arziki mai kyau. Kuma lalle ne Allah, haƙĩƙa, Shĩ ne Mafi alhẽrin m&atilde;su azurt&atilde;wa.';
$t[59] = 'Lalle ne, Yan&atilde; shigar da su a wata mashiga wadda z&atilde; su yarda da ita. Kuma lalle ne Allah, haƙĩƙa Masani ne, Mai haƙuri.';
$t[60] = 'Wancan! Kuma wanda ya r&atilde;ma az&atilde;ba da mis&atilde;lin abin da aka yi masa, sa\'an nan kuma aka z&atilde;lunce shi, lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; taimakon sa. Lalle ne Allah haƙĩƙa Mai y&atilde;fẽwa ne, Mai g&atilde;fara.';
$t[61] = 'Wancan! sab&otilde;da Allah Yan&atilde; shigar da dare a cikin yini, kuma Yan&atilde; shigar da yini a cikin dare, kuma lalle, Allah Mai jĩ ne, Mai gani.';
$t[62] = 'Wancan! sab&otilde;da lalle ne Allah, shĩ ne Gaskiya, kuma lalle ne, abin da suke kira waninSa shi ne ƙarya. Kuma lalle ne Allah, Shĩ ne Maɗaukaki, Mai girma.';
$t[63] = 'Ashe, ba ka gani ba, lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; saukar da ruwa daga sama, sai ƙasa ta w&atilde;yi gari k&otilde;riya? Lalle Allah Mai tausasawa ne, Mai ƙididdigewa.';
$t[64] = 'Abin da ke a cikin sammai, da abin da ke a cikin ƙasa, Nasa ne, kuma lalle ne Allah, haƙĩƙa, Shi ne wadatacce, G&otilde;dadde.';
$t[65] = 'Shin ba ka gani ba, lalle ne Allah Ya h&otilde;re muku abin da yake a cikin ƙasa, kuma jir&atilde;ge sun&atilde; gud&atilde;na a cikin tẽku, da umurninSa kuma Yan&atilde; riƙe sama d&otilde;min kada ta f&atilde;ɗi a kan ƙasa f&atilde;ce da izninsa? Lalle ne Allah ga mut&atilde;ne haƙĩƙa, Mai tausayi ne, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[66] = 'Kuma shĩ ne wanda Ya r&atilde;ya ku, sa\'an nan kuma Yan&atilde; matar da ku, sa\'an nan kuma Yan&atilde; r&atilde;yar da ku. Lalle mutum, haƙĩƙa, mai k&atilde;firci ne.';
$t[67] = 'Ga k&otilde;wace al\'umma Mun sanya wurin yanka, su ne masu yin baiko gare Shi, sab&otilde;da haka, kada su yi maka j&atilde;yayya a cikin al\'amarin (hadaya). Kuma ka yi kira zuwa ga Ubangijinka lalle kai kana a kan shiriya madaidaiciya.';
$t[68] = 'Kuma idan sun yi maka jid&atilde;li, sai ka ce: &quot;Allah ne Mafi sani game da abin da kuke aikat&atilde;wa.&quot;';
$t[69] = '&quot;Allah ne zai yi hukunci a tsak&atilde;ninku, a R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma a cikin abin da kuka kasance a cikinsa kun&atilde; s&atilde;ɓawa jũna.&quot;';
$t[70] = 'Ashe, ba ka sani ba, lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; sanin abin da yake a cikin sama da ƙasa? Lalle ne wancan yan&atilde; cikin Littafi lalle wancan ga Allah mai sauƙi ne.';
$t[71] = 'Kuma sun&atilde; baut&atilde;wa baicin Allah, abin da (Allah) bai saukar da wani dalili ba game da shi, kuma abin da b&atilde; su da wani ilmi game da shi, kuma b&atilde;bu wani mai taimako ga azz&atilde;lumai.';
$t[72] = 'Kuma idan an&atilde; karanta &atilde;y&otilde;yinMu bayyanannu a kansu kan&atilde; sanin abin ƙy&atilde;ma a cikin fusk&otilde;kin waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta sun&atilde; kusa su yi danƙa ga waɗanda ke kar&atilde;tun ay&otilde;yinMu a kansu. Ka ce: &quot;Shin to in gaya muku abin da yake mafi sharri daga wannan? (Ita ce) Wuta.&quot; Allah Y&atilde; yi alkawarinta ga waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta. Kuma mak&otilde;marsu ta mũnana.';
$t[73] = '&quot;Ya ku mut&atilde;ne! An buga wani mis&atilde;li, sai ku saur&atilde;ra zuwa gare shi. Lalle ne waɗanda kuke kira baicin Allah, b&atilde; z&atilde; su halitta ƙud&atilde; ba, k&otilde; da sun t&atilde;ru gare shi, kuma idan ƙud&atilde;n ya ƙw&atilde;ce musu wani abu, b&atilde; z&atilde; su kuɓutar da shi ba daga gare shi. Mai nẽma da wanda ake nẽman gare shi sun raunana.&quot;';
$t[74] = 'Ba su ƙaddara wa Allah hakkin girmanSa ba. Lalle ne Allah, haƙĩƙa, Mai ƙarfi ne, Mabuw&atilde;yi.';
$t[75] = 'Allah n&atilde; z&atilde;ɓen Manzanni daga mal&atilde;\'iku kuma daga mut&atilde;ne. Lalle Allah, Mai ji ne, Mai gani.';
$t[76] = 'Yan&atilde; sanin abin da ke gaba gare su da abin da ke b&atilde;yansu, kuma zuwa ga Allah ake mayar da al\'amura.';
$t[77] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku yi rukũ\'i, kuma ku yi sujada, kuma ku bauta wa Ubangijinku, kuma ku aikata alhẽri, tsamm&atilde;ninku, ku sami babban rabo.';
$t[78] = 'Kuma ku yi jih&atilde;di a cikin (al\'amarin) Allah, hakkin Jih&atilde;dinSa. shĩ ne Ya z&atilde;ɓe ku alh&atilde;li kuwa bai sanya wani ƙunci ba a kanku a cikin addĩni. Bisa ƙudurcẽwar ubanku Ibr&atilde;hĩm, shĩ ne ya yi muku sũna Musulmi daga gab&atilde;nin haka. Kuma a cikin wannan (Litt&atilde;fi ya yi muku sũna Musulmi), d&otilde;min Manzo ya kasance mai shaida a kanku, kũ kuma ku kasancem&atilde;su shaida a kan mut&atilde;ne. Sab&otilde;da haka ku tsayar da salla kuma ku b&atilde;yar da zakka kuma ku amince da Allah, Shi ne Majiɓincinku. S&atilde;b&otilde;da haka m&atilde;dalla da Shi Ya zama Majiɓinci, m&atilde;dalla da Shi ya zama Mai taimako.';
?>